        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-38280152" class="vote-count">21</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-38280152" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="38280152">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiaotaizi/">Zitsunari</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2008-04-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">先生所论米道、桃源诸事，皆有发明。万氏文笔固使人厌，其尤可恨者，“前言”谓先生之学术“向马克思主义史学转变”，实荒谬绝伦，可不复言。 080416-080425</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="790533160">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-790533160" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-790533160" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="790533160">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chariot/">小车</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-03-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">第一次读的时候，是把里面很多结论当做定论来看的。现在再读，发现问题很多，逻辑不确定、材料支撑不足的地方比比皆是。但是更加觉得陈先生了不起，从纷乱的史料当中，把许多看似无关的资料关联起来，发掘出新的线索，指出新的出路。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1201327951">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1201327951" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1201327951" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1201327951">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
